This multi-tasking palette features expertly coordinated color combinations of intensely pigmented matte lip cream that gives you the coverage of a matte lipstick and blendability of a blusher. Each shade stands alone or can be blended together for a customized shade. When you can't decide on just one lip shade to buy, don't. Just pick up one of these lip palettes instead.
